Kaya...

654
00:38:08.667 --> 00:38:10.400
I mean...

655
00:38:12.567 --> 00:38:14.236
Ano ang mali? nasaktan ka ba

656
00:38:14.236 --> 00:38:15.700
ito ay...

657
00:38:15.700 --> 00:38:16.700
- Ang tiyan ko...
- Tiyan?

658
00:38:16.700 --> 00:38:19.133
