664
00:38:33.067 --> 00:38:34.700
Tagapangalaga para kay Jang Hui Won?

665
00:38:34.700 --> 00:38:35.733
Oo.

666
00:38:35.733 --> 00:38:37.900
Mangyaring punan ang form na ito.

667
00:38:46.000 --> 00:38:48.833
<i>Mukhang naging ang ina
