[Min Uk]

676
00:39:28.967 --> 00:39:31.700
Oo, anong nangyari? Naging maayos ba ang lahat?

677
00:39:31.700 --> 00:39:33.400
<i>Kamusta?</i>

678
00:39:34.267 --> 00:39:36.467
Hindi ba ito ang telepono ni Jang Hui Won?

679
00:39:36.467 --> 00:39:39.367
