715
00:42:08.667 --> 00:42:10.600
Alam mo ba kung ano ang ginagawa niya?

716
00:42:10.600 --> 00:42:12.500
- Isang tteokbokki dito, pakiusap.
- Pinagulong omelet.

717
00:42:12.500 --> 00:42:13.767
Isang rolled omelet din, please.

718
00:42:13.767 --> 00:42:15.367
Nakuha ko. Gagawin ko itong masarap.

719
00:42:15.367 --> 00:42:17.433
- Oo.
- Oo.

720
00:42:17.433 --> 00:42:19.167
Maghintay ka.

721
00:42:21.800 --> 00:42:24.604
Talagang hindi mo masasabi kay Min Uk

722
00:42:24.604 --> 00:42:28.533
