753
00:43:29.633 --> 00:43:30.633
Ganun din ba noong araw na iyon?

754
00:43:30.633 --> 00:43:32.900
Bastos at walang konsiderasyon?

755
00:43:32.900 --> 00:43:35.800
Well, saglit ko lang siya nakita,
kaya hindi ko maalala...

756
00:43:35.800 --> 00:43:38.967
Ugh, seryoso, nasaan siya
kahit makakilala ka ng ganyang lalaki?

757
00:43:38.967 --> 00:43:42.267
Nga pala, pumunta ka dito
para itanong lang yan?

758
00:43:42.267 --> 00:43:45.567
Gusto mo ba si Hui Won o ano?

759
00:43:45.567 --> 00:43:47.167
- Ako?
- Ibig kong sabihin,

760
00:43:47.167 --> 00:43:50.233
