762
00:43:52.567 --> 00:43:54.300
Hoy, ikaw!

763
00:43:55.367 --> 00:43:57.867
Matagal ko na siyang kilala.

764
00:43:57.867 --> 00:44:03.533
Alam mo kung paano siya. meron ba
