765
00:44:03.533 --> 00:44:05.733
Well, totoo naman.

766
00:44:07.833 --> 00:44:10.200
Pero pumunta ka dito para itanong yan?

767
00:44:19.700 --> 00:44:21.933
Kaya kong pumunta mag-isa para sa check-up.

768
00:44:21.933 --> 00:44:23.600
Maghintay ka.

769
00:44:23.600 --> 00:44:25.333
Oo?

770
00:44:26.900 --> 00:44:28.667
ano?

771
00:44:41.167 --> 00:44:43.633
Paumanhin, ngunit ito ba ay...

772
00:44:43.633 --> 00:44:45.200
ha?

773
00:44:45.200 --> 00:44:48.764
Hindi, akala ko buntis ka.

774
00:44:48.764 --> 00:44:50.067
Ah.

775
00:44:50.067 --> 00:44:52.188
Ito ay hindi alkoholiko.

776
00:44:52.188 --> 00:44:53.700
Oh.

777
00:44:53.700 --> 00:44:57.233
Pinagagalitan talaga ako ng mga matatanda dito
marami dahil dito.

778
00:44:57.233 --> 00:45:00.500
Kahit anong paliwanag ko
ito ay isang inumin lamang, hindi alkohol, hindi kukulangin,

779
00:45:00.500 --> 00:45:03.933
